args:
As the group pushes through a blizzard, Notte
hears an unknown voice in her head right before
an avalanche strikes! The scattered party is
troubled by illusions that reflect their anxieties,
but Gatov manages to lead everyone to a
nearby cave—except for the prince and Luca.
*pant* *pant* We've climbed quite far,\nyet there's nothing but snow as far as\nthe eye can see...
And the steepness of this path is not\naided by the blizzard that seems to be\nblowing in, either.

Visibility is poor. Observable range
has dropped most significantly.
▷We can hardly see our own hands
in front of our faces!◁
Just keep calling out to one another\nso we don't get separated!
Oh man, my wings are totes icing over...\nI can't even fly right in this junk!
I'll warm you with my flames, Notte!
What the hey?! Who said that?!
Somebody's talking to me!\nSomebody weird, I mean!
I didn't hear nothin' over... Uh oh.\nIs this one'a them illusion dealies?
Don't let it trick you, Notte!\nIgnore the voice!
Okay, but how? It's inside my HEAD!
Alert: High winds and snow incoming.\n▷Oh no! The blizzard is getting worse!◁
Everyone stay as low as you can!
Don't have to tell me twice!
This damn wind is gonna blow us\nclear off the mountain!
Hmph! This is just a little flurry.\nStill, everyone hide behind me!
I'll channel the fires of my love\nand blow all this away!
Mym, you rule! The snow's melting!
The legendary Flamewyrm shows her\nquality once more!
Wait, that sound... We're in danger!
Wh-whoa! You've got to be kidding me!
Looks like I've escaped serious harm.
The blizzard seems to have passed.\nHow long was I out, exactly...?
I'd best find the others as soon as I can.
Hmmm? That figure... It can't be!
It is His Majesty King Alberius!
How have you come to be here,\nYour Majesty?!
Oh, I have been waiting so very long\nfor a chance to see you again...
Your Majesty, what's wrong?!\nAre you wounded?
This stems entirely from your arrogance.\nYour selfishness.
The king has taken all responsibility upon\nhimself, and even now endures the agony\nof the Blood Casket alone.
N-no! Your Majesty, I will heal you!\nI will ease your pain!
Please don't go, Your Majesty! Please...
You beheld that brutal spectacle, yes?\nA face twisted with pain and anguish.
You have done this thing, Cleo.\nYou have slaughtered your king!
I am! I'm in my own body!\nI've returned to my own body!
But my body stopped functioning when I\ngave Laxi my heart, so how can any of\nthis be happening...?
Me? What did I...? Oh no! No no no,\nthis can't be happening!
Did I...do this to you?\nIs this how I got my body back?
Was that Laxi's voice?! What's going on?!\nDammit, this is all my fault!
The video you're seeing is a result of our\nvisual and aural circuits being hijacked.\nIt is merely a false illusion.
Mascula's visual circuit restored.\nNew issue confirmed in ego circuit.\nInitiating repairs.
▷Laxi, you saved me. I'm so sorry\nI put you through all that trouble.◁
......Do you want your own body, Mascula?
▷Um, well... Look, I don't want you to\nmisunderstand what that means, okay?◁
▷I'm happy with our situation right now—\nmostly because I feel like it helped to\ndeepen our friendship. But...◁
▷Well, sometimes I have...thoughts.\nLike, maybe I could be more useful\nto everyone if I had my own body?◁
▷I'm sorry, Laxi. It's not about you.◁
Your apologies are unnecessary;\nI believe I understand your feelings.\n...Continuing repairs.
(I'll never forget this sight.\nIt is my burden to bear.)
Sheila...it's the real you.\nSo I've come back.
Ah, you can't even see the illusions.
Just be patient for a little longer.\nI'm going to get you back—I swear it.
Well, enough woolgathering.\nWe need to find everyone else.
Yeah—just remembered some stupid crap\nfrom back when I was a merc, is all.
No tellin' where we'd be now\nif Gatov didn't save our butts.
Did you not see an illusion, Zena?\n'Cause I've basically been fine except\nfor that weirdo voice from earlier.
Oh, I'm already quite accustomed to\nrepeating days of unrequited desires\nwithout end.
Oh...right. Sorry...\nI wonder how the others are doing.\nI hope they're okay.
Cleo and Laxi! Oh man, that's a huge\npiece of good news right there.
▷......◁\nMascula is still experiencing the effects\nof the illusion on his ego circuit.
Then I take it the three of you\nsaw something painful as well.
*sigh* The blizzard has gotten worse—just\nlook what a mess it made of my outfit!
How did things go for you, Chelle?\nAside from the outfit, I mean.
I looked everywhere I could reach,\nbut didn't find anyone.
At present, my brother and Luca\nare still unaccounted for.
This storm is going to make further\nsearching difficult; we've no choice but\nto wait here until the weather calms.
Then we'll just stay put and pray\nthey are both safe and sound.
Oh man, where could they be...?
(They say the illusions of the Faewood\nwork their most potent magics on those\nwith unhealed wounds in their hearts.)
({player_name}...\nPlease hang on until help can reach you...)
